id: pm-90hp
title: "pm todos import: positional source arg silently ignored + folder-not-found error omits --folder flag (beads parity)"
description: "Repro (sandbox, pm-todos installed): 'pm todos import todos.md' accepts the positional, ignores it, and errors 'Todos source folder not found at .../.pm/todos' without mentioning the --folder flag. Compare pm beads import whose error says 'Use --file <path> or --file - for stdin'. Two fixes: (1) reject or honor the unexpected positional (an agent passing a file path gets no signal it was ignored); (2) include 'Use --folder <path>' in the folder-not-found guidance. Bonus: 'pm todos import --help' prints flags twice (Options section + Extension-provided flags section) — duplicated tokens."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 3
tags[4]: agent-ux,dogfood-2026-06-12,packages,todos
created_at: "2026-06-12T16:19:38.893Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-19T12:00:49.532Z"
author: maintainer-agent
parent: pm-mpbb
dependencies[1]{id,kind,created_at,author,source_kind}:
  pm-i35t,related,"2026-06-19T10:14:40.955Z",claude-code-agent,null
comments[5]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-19T11:00:47.672Z",claude-code-agent,"Implemented in feat/agent-ergonomics-cmd-suggestions-importer-ux. Root cause: importer/exporter commands dispatch through wrapProgramActionsForExtensionHandlers -> runActiveCommandHandler (handled=true short-circuits), bypassing the dynamic-action validateDynamicExtensionCommandInvocation, so unexpected positionals were silently ignored. Fixes: (1) wrappedActionHandler now rejects unexpected positionals for IMPORTER/EXPORTER command paths that declare no arguments (new isImporterOrExporterCommandPath gate keyed off registrations.importers/exporters; free-form registerCommand commands and arg-declaring commands like calendar are untouched). New collectLoosePositionalArgs (extension-command-options.ts) counts only true operands so leaked undeclared --flag tokens are not miscounted. (2) failure_hints now append to the too-many/missing-required arity errors; todos importer/exporter declare a 'Use --folder <path>' hint. (3) folder-not-found error in todos runtime.ts/.js now includes the --folder guidance. (4) Help dedup: extension flags registered as real options no longer ALSO render in a duplicate 'Extension-provided flags:' after-text (new buildResidualDynamicExtensionFlagHelp). Tests: in-process guard test in cli-main-errors.spec.ts, collectLoosePositionalArgs in main-loose-options.spec.ts, residual-help + arity-hint assertions, todos-extension.spec.ts folder-hint, integration acme/beads/todos help dedup. Docs: SDK.md importer positional contract. 100% coverage retained."
  "2026-06-19T11:23:29.454Z",codex-cli-agent,"Evidence: continued branch feat/agent-ergonomics-cmd-suggestions-importer-ux on 2026-06-19. Verified focused UX tests passed (5 files, 255 tests), temp-dir smoke confirmed todos import positional rejection, missing-folder --folder guidance, and no duplicate Extension-provided flags section. Repo gates passed after follow-up: pnpm quality:static, pnpm typecheck, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage = 100/100/100/100 (230 files, 4653 tests)."
  "2026-06-19T11:35:09.129Z",codex-cli-agent,"Review follow-up: addressed Gemini parser-safety suggestion in collectLoosePositionalArgs by ensuring any parsed option token advances by at least one slot, preventing non-advancing parser results without adding an unreachable branch to the 100% coverage gate."
  "2026-06-19T11:41:43.373Z",codex-cli-agent,"Verification after review follow-up: focused tests passed (tests/unit/cli/cli-main-errors.spec.ts + main-loose-options.spec.ts, 130 tests), pnpm typecheck passed, pnpm quality:static passed, and node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed at 100/100/100/100 (230 files, 4653 tests)."
  "2026-06-19T12:00:49.532Z",codex-cli-agent,"Review follow-up: tightened importer/exporter wrapped dispatch validation so declared positional arguments are validated before extension handlers as well as no-arg importers. Regression coverage added for valid declared args, too many declared args, and missing required declared args. Verification: focused CLI tests passed (130 tests), pnpm typecheck passed, pnpm quality:static passed, node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage passed at 100/100/100/100 (230 files, 4653 tests)."
close_reason: "Implemented importer/exporter positional rejection, failure_hints guidance, todos --folder runtime guidance, and extension help deduplication, verified with temp-dir todos smoke, focused UX tests, typecheck, static/docstring quality gate, and full coverage 100/100/100/100."
body: ""
